{"per_page":10,"total":15,"current":11,"data":[{"title":"Git Branch(分支)","date":"2018-08-09T18:46:00.000Z","excerpt":"<ol>\n<li><p>查看分支</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git branch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>创建分支</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git branch &lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>切换分支</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git checkout &lt;branch-name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>","link":"post/188","categories":["Git"]},{"title":"PLSQL添加新的链接数据库（DBLINK方式）","date":"2018-08-08T00:21:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h4 id=\"其实就是（创建新的DBlink即可）\"><strong>其实就是（创建新的DBlink即可）</strong><a href=\"post/179#其实就是（创建新的DBlink即可）\"></a></h4><h4 id=\"1、安装orcale客户端\">1、安装orcale客户端<a href=\"post/179#1、安装orcale客户端\"></a></h4><p>这里我安装的是11g版本的<br>下载地址：<br><a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/otn/nt/oracle11g/112010/win32_11gR2_client.zip\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://download.oracle.com/otn/nt/oracle11g/112010/win32_11gR2_client.zip</a><br>安装教程：<br><a href=\"https://jingyan.baidu.com/article/14bd256e6fc34fbb6c26127e.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://jingyan.baidu.com/article/14bd256e6fc34fbb6c26127e.html</a></p>\n<h4 id=\"2、添加DBLINK\">2、添加DBLINK<a href=\"post/179#2、添加DBLINK\"></a></h4><p><strong>按照图片顺序添加即可</strong><br></p>","link":"post/179","categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"Centos7上卸载MariaDB数据库和本地Navicat连接不上虚拟机数据库","date":"2018-08-06T03:35:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/178","categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":"linux_CentOS7_yum时出错，Could not retrieve mirrorlist","date":"2018-08-05T05:38:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/176","categories":["Liunx"]},{"title":" JQuery点击事件回到页面顶部效果","date":"2018-07-30T22:20:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/172","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"php未序列化无法插入数据库","date":"2018-07-26T03:38:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p><strong>详细的php序列化和反序列化知识</strong><br><a href=\"http://www.php.net/manual/zh/function.serialize.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://www.php.net/manual/zh/function.serialize.php</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"错误：\">错误：<a href=\"post/171#错误：\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/4240588291.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>","link":"post/171","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"jQuery 属性操作 - attr() 方法","date":"2018-07-25T02:13:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>项目代码,需要点击图片后，弹出dailog窗口，显示完整图片</p>\n<p>html部分<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;div class=&quot; user_upload_images&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;img src=&quot;&#123;php echo tomedia($item[&apos;content_image&apos;])&#125;&quot; class=&quot;imgg&quot; style=&quot;width:40px;height:40px;padding:1px;border:1px solid #ccc;&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">//dialog提示框</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div id=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;img src=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;show_big_image&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">//使用jqueryUi</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;//apps.bdimg.com/libs/jqueryui/1.10.4/css/jquery-ui.min.css&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script src=&quot;//apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/1.10.2/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script src=&quot;//apps.bdimg.com/libs/jqueryui/1.10.4/jquery-ui.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>js部分<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$(function () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       $(&quot;#dialog&quot;).dialog(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           autoOpen: false,</span><br><span class=\"line\">           show: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">         </span><br><span class=\"line\">           &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">           hide: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           </span><br><span class=\"line\">           &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">       $(&quot;.imgg&quot;).click(function () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           $(&quot;#dialog&quot;).dialog(&quot;open&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t//当点击 class=imgg 的标签时，将id=show_big_image标签中的src属性赋值成 class=imgg 的标签中的src属性的值</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t$(&quot;#show_big_image&quot;).attr(&quot;src&quot;,$(this).attr(&quot;src&quot;));</span><br><span class=\"line\">       &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/164","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"mybatis中的事务管理器 TransactionManager基础知识","date":"2018-07-23T05:55:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>transactionManager提供了两个实现类，但是这两个实现类必须实现Transaction这个接口<br>Transaction中包含了三个重要的方法：commit（提交）、rollback（回滚），close（关闭）<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">public interfance Transaction&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   Connection getConnection() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  void commit() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  void rollback() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  void close() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  Integer getTimeout() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/159","categories":["Mybatis"]},{"title":"php中判断一个时间是今天的时间","date":"2018-07-23T01:57:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/158","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"git 添加文件未识别","date":"2018-07-16T23:07:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/157","categories":["Git"]}]}